'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly'''''  ( French   ) ni filime yo muri Gabon ya 2016 iyobowe na [[Samantha Biffot]]<ref>The African Who Wanted to Fly | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › the-african-who-want...</ref> . Igice gishingiye kubuzima bwa Luc Bendza . Filime yakozwe mu ndimi ebyiri, [[Gishinwa|Igishinwa]] [[Igifaransa|n'Igifaransa]], kandi yari ifite insanganyamatsiko [[Icyongereza|y'icyongereza.]]<ref>This event has passed. The African Who Wanted To Fly (africanfilmny.org)</ref> 

== Umusaruro ==
'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly''''' yakozwe na Neon Rouge, afatanije na Theatre Company Theatre ( [[Ubufaransa]] )<ref>The African Who Wanted to Fly - Africa Is a Country <nowiki>https://africasacountry.com</nowiki> › 2017/05 › the-african-wh...</ref>.  Scenese yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Gabon]], no mu Bushinwa. Umuziki wari ugizwe nindirimbo zishinwa.<ref>African who wanted to fly (The) - SPLA <nowiki>http://www.spla.pro</nowiki> › file.film.african-who-wanted-to-fl...</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Urebye filime Big Boss, umwana wo muri [[Gabon]] yavumbuye Kung Fu ahitamo kujya mu [[Ubushinwa|Bushinwa]] afite imyaka 15 gusa<ref>The African Who Wanted To Fly - BAM <nowiki>https://www.bam.org</nowiki> › film › the-african-who-wanted-t...</ref>. Yize ko azaba umunyafrica wambere wize ibihangano bya Kung Fu. Ahinduka inararibonye muri yo<ref>African Film Festival: The African Who Wanted to Fly - Duke ... <nowiki>https://igs.duke.edu</nowiki> › events › african-film-festival-afric...</ref>.

== Kwerekanwa ==

